Delete - Vector Store File```HTTPDELETE https://{endpoint}/openai/vector_stores/{vector_store_id}/files/{file_id}?api-version=2024-05-01-preview```Delete a vector store file. This will remove the file from the vector store but the file itself won't be deleted. To delete the file, use the delete file endpoint.### URI Parameters| Name | In | Required | Type | Description ||------|------|----------|------|-----------|| endpoint | path | Yes | string
url | Supported Azure OpenAI endpoints (protocol and hostname, for example: `https://aoairesource.openai.azure.com`.
